<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Boba Shop System</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka:wght@500;600;700&family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css">
</head>
<body>
    <main class="landing-shell">
        <section class="landing-card">
            <h1>FSH Boba</h1>

            <div class="portal-grid">
                <a class="portal-button cashier" href="/loginCashier">
                    <h2>Cashier Login</h2>
                    <p>Open the point-of-sale flow for team members handling orders in person.</p>
                </a>

                <a class="portal-button manager" href="/loginManager">
                    <h2>Manager Login</h2>
                    <p>Head to reports, employees, inventory, and the rest of the admin tools.</p>
                </a>

                <a class="portal-button kiosk" href="/kiosk">
                    <h2>Self-Serving Kiosk</h2>
                    <p>Launch the customer-facing ordering experience.</p>
                </a>

                <a class="portal-button menu-board" href="/menu-board">
                    <h2>Menu Board</h2>
                    <p>Open the static chalkboard menu display for guests.</p>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
